document.discussion_title: Restaurant fire on East Bay Drive
document.topic_text: East Bay Drive back open after restaurant fire WTSP 10:11 AM. EST April 25, 2016 Photo from the scene of the fire at German Deli restaurant on East Bay Drive in Largo. (WTSP) (Photo: Falzon, Kristin) East Bay Drive is back open late Monday morning after a fire that broke out at a German Deli restaurant. Fire investigators are looking into the cause of the fire.
